00:32:40,868 --> 00:32:43,168
<font color="yellow">What is everyone looking for her?</font>

504
00:32:43,698 --> 00:32:46,398
<font color="yellow">Is she an important part of this office?</font>

505
00:32:46,798 --> 00:32:50,168
