507
00:32:54,638 --> 00:32:55,838
<font color="yellow">She's coming in late today.</font>

508
00:32:56,238 --> 00:32:57,298
<font color="yellow">- Why? - Why?</font>

509
00:32:57,598 --> 00:33:00,498
