531
00:34:21,338 --> 00:34:24,968
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. I should've been there. I had to work.</font>

532
00:34:25,668 --> 00:34:27,168
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about it.</font>

533
00:34:28,198 --> 00:34:29,538
<font color="yellow">By the way,</font>

