00:35:04,668 --> 00:35:05,668
<font color="yellow">Grandma.</font>

545
00:35:06,098 --> 00:35:07,868
<font color="yellow">I even received the prize money.</font>

546
00:35:08,868 --> 00:35:11,438
<font color="yellow">My goodness. You did?</font>

547
00:35:13,268 --> 00:35:15,808
<font color="yellow">I received 5,000 dollars.</font>

548
00:35:18,238 --> 00:35:22,068
<font color="yellow">Gosh. My baby did well.</font>

549
00:35:22,808 --> 00:35:24,308
<font color="yellow">I'm so proud of you.</font>

