00:36:20,698 --> 00:36:22,068
<font color="yellow">Go upstairs.</font>

562
00:36:22,638 --> 00:36:24,268
<font color="yellow">It's a talk between two men.</font>

563
00:36:44,498 --> 00:36:47,568
<font color="yellow">So how does it feel to stay at home for a few days?</font>

