565
00:36:53,308 --> 00:36:55,438
<font color="yellow">I didn't accept your resignation yet.</font>

566
00:36:56,068 --> 00:36:57,198
<font color="yellow">Keep your manner.</font>

567
00:36:58,638 --> 00:36:59,698
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

568
00:37:01,168 --> 00:37:03,638
<font color="yellow">Writer Jo said...</font>

