00:37:11,468 --> 00:37:12,968
<font color="yellow">that she will terminate the contract.</font>

572
00:37:13,938 --> 00:37:17,368
<font color="yellow">She's temperamental and grumpy.</font>

573
00:37:18,438 --> 00:37:21,538
<font color="yellow">Tell her to do whatever she wants.</font>

