00:37:21,868 --> 00:37:24,368
<font color="yellow">However, what will you do with...</font>

575
00:37:24,538 --> 00:37:27,568
<font color="yellow">the schedule you coordinated under her name?</font>

576
00:37:27,938 --> 00:37:31,668
<font color="yellow">If we can't deliver our side of the bargain,</font>

