00:37:32,468 --> 00:37:34,338
<font color="yellow">we will have to stop our...</font>

578
00:37:35,438 --> 00:37:36,768
<font color="yellow">contents-related business forever.</font>

579
00:37:37,398 --> 00:37:39,368
<font color="yellow">You might think you handed in...</font>

