00:38:00,768 --> 00:38:02,668
<font color="yellow">to keep being stubborn?</font>

589
00:38:09,698 --> 00:38:11,038
<font color="yellow">You're so arrogant.</font>

590
00:38:12,038 --> 00:38:14,168
<font color="yellow">He resigned from our company?</font>

