593
00:38:21,238 --> 00:38:22,808
<font color="yellow">Later I will find something on him...</font>

594
00:38:23,308 --> 00:38:24,968
<font color="yellow">and send him to jail.</font>

595
00:38:26,268 --> 00:38:29,268
<font color="yellow">All sorts of things happen when you produce a drama.</font>

596
00:38:30,138 --> 00:38:33,738
<font color="yellow">I'm going to teach him a lesson.</font>

