00:38:38,308 --> 00:38:41,238
<font color="yellow">and later, I will make sure that he ends up in jail.</font>

599
00:38:41,898 --> 00:38:44,068
<font color="yellow">That was arrogant of him.</font>

600
00:38:44,438 --> 00:38:46,538
<font color="yellow">How dare he act like that?</font>

