00:39:02,138 --> 00:39:03,238
<font color="yellow">Get in.</font>

605
00:39:30,498 --> 00:39:33,098
<font color="yellow">- Please enjoy your beverages. - Thank you.</font>

606
00:39:38,898 --> 00:39:39,938
<font color="yellow">Jeong Eun.</font>

607
00:39:41,598 --> 00:39:44,338
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon, what brings you here at this hour?</font>

608
00:39:47,468 --> 00:39:48,538
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

609
00:39:52,038 --> 00:39:53,468
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

610
00:39:56,938 --> 00:39:57,938
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon.</font>

611
00:39:59,308 --> 00:40:00,308
<font color="yellow">What do you...</font>

612
00:40:01,698 --> 00:40:03,338
<font color="yellow">like about Lee Hyun Woo?</font>

613
00:40:05,198 --> 00:40:06,468
<font color="yellow">Why are you bringing this up?</font>

