00:40:06,738 --> 00:40:08,368
<font color="yellow">I was just curious.</font>

615
00:40:12,268 --> 00:40:13,398
<font color="yellow">I don't think...</font>

616
00:40:13,898 --> 00:40:15,598
<font color="yellow">he's such a good person.</font>

