00:40:28,198 --> 00:40:29,598
<font color="yellow">this is a secret.</font>

621
00:40:30,198 --> 00:40:33,438
<font color="yellow">I met him in New York three years ago.</font>

622
00:40:34,238 --> 00:40:36,438
<font color="yellow">I've been watching him ever since.</font>

623
00:40:37,068 --> 00:40:39,368
<font color="yellow">- Really? - Yes.</font>

624
00:40:39,668 --> 00:40:43,498
<font color="yellow">At the time, he was the CEO of an investment bank on Wall Street.</font>

625
00:40:44,598 --> 00:40:46,868
<font color="yellow">He's now lost everything.</font>

