00:40:51,068 --> 00:40:53,168
<font color="yellow">with stocks and then lost everything.</font>

628
00:40:53,198 --> 00:40:56,068
<font color="yellow">But he's a good person. He's very good-hearted.</font>

629
00:40:56,468 --> 00:40:58,268
<font color="yellow">He treats me well,</font>

