00:41:03,538 --> 00:41:05,338
<font color="yellow">Yes. Why?</font>

633
00:41:08,138 --> 00:41:09,168
<font color="yellow">It's nothing.</font>

634
00:41:51,638 --> 00:41:53,398
<font color="yellow">I am sorry. I am sorry.</font>

635
00:42:11,738 --> 00:42:12,968
<font color="yellow">- You're here again. - Yes.</font>

636
00:42:13,498 --> 00:42:15,138
<font color="yellow">- Hello. - Hello.</font>

